{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/posts/algorithm/react with daum-map.1/","result":{"data":{"logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","width":400,"height":128,"src":"/static/2b5eaa0de166a8b5faebad4955c2200c/3891b/ghost-logo.png","srcSet":"/static/2b5eaa0de166a8b5faebad4955c2200c/3891b/ghost-logo.png 1x"}}},"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2 id=\"키-발급\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%82%A4-%EB%B0%9C%EA%B8%89\" aria-label=\"키 발급 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>키 발급</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://developers.kakao.com/\">카카오 개발자사이트</a>에가서 가입후 키발급을 받자</p>\n<h2 id=\"적용하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"적용하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>적용하기</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-publicindexhtml에-다음-지도-api를-스크립트로-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-publicindexhtml%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%A4%EC%9D%8C-%EC%A7%80%EB%8F%84-api%EB%A5%BC-%EC%8A%A4%ED%81%AC%EB%A6%BD%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%9C-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"1 publicindexhtml에 다음 지도 api를 스크립트로 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. <code>public/index.html</code>에 다음 지도 api를 스크립트로 추가</h3>\n<deckgo-highlight-code html  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">&lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot; src=&quot;//dapi.kakao.com/v2/maps/sdk.js?appkey=발급받은키값&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<h3 id=\"2-사용하려는-컴포넌트에-추가\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%A0%A4%EB%8A%94-%EC%BB%B4%ED%8F%AC%EB%84%8C%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90-%EC%B6%94%EA%B0%80\" aria-label=\"2 사용하려는 컴포넌트에 추가 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. 사용하려는 컴포넌트에 추가</h3>\n<deckgo-highlight-code typescript  theme=\"one-dark\"  highlight-lines=\"\">\n          <code slot=\"code\">import * as React from &#39;react&#39;;\r\n\r\ndeclare var daum:any;\r\n\r\nclass Map extends React.Component {\r\n  componentDidMount() {\r\n    const el = document.getElementById(&#39;map&#39;);\r\n    let daumMap = new daum.maps.Map(el, {\r\n      center: new daum.maps.LatLng(33.450701, 126.570667),\r\n    });\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  render() {\r\n    return (\r\n      &lt;React.Fragment&gt;\r\n        &lt;div className=&quot;Map&quot; id=&quot;map&quot; style=&quot;width:1000px;height:500px&quot;/&gt;\r\n\r\n      &lt;/React.Fragment&gt;\r\n    );\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n\r\nexport default Map;\r\n</code>\n        </deckgo-highlight-code>\n<p>이 때 TSlint가 daum키워드 때문에 계속 오류를 내뿜는다. 이렇게 써드파티 라이브러리를 타입스크립트에서 사용할 땐 <a href=\"http://www.albertgao.xyz/2016/08/10/how-to-use-a-third-party-library-in-typescript-with-or-without-its-type-definition-file/\">여러방법</a>으로 피할 수 있지만 간단히 <code>declare var someValue:any</code>를 사용 할 수도 있다.</p>\n<p>리액트에는 여러 라이프사이클이 존재한다. 그 중 <code>componentDidMount()</code>은 컴포넌트가 화면에 나타나게 됐을 때 호출된다. 주로 DOM을 사용하는 외부 라이브러리 연동을 하거나 데이터를 요청하기위해 ajax요청을 하거나, DOM 속성을 읽거나 직접 변경하는 작업을 진행할 수 있다.</p>\n<p><code>... declared but its value is never read</code> 이 오류 메세지가 뜬다면 <code>tsconfig.json</code>파일에서 <code>noUnusedLocals</code>를 <code>false</code>로 바꾸면된다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"참고한-링크\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B0%B8%EA%B3%A0%ED%95%9C-%EB%A7%81%ED%81%AC\" aria-label=\"참고한 링크 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>참고한 링크</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://velopert.com/3631\">누구든지 하는 리액트 5편: LifeCycle API</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.albertgao.xyz/2016/08/10/how-to-use-a-third-party-library-in-typescript-with-or-without-its-type-definition-file/\">How to use a third party library in Typescript with or without its type definition file?</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/issues/19700\">https://github.com/Microsoft/TypeScript/issues/19700</a></li>\n</ul>","htmlAst":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"키-발급","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%ED%82%A4-%EB%B0%9C%EA%B8%89","ariaLabel":"키 발급 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z"},"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"키 발급"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"p","properties":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"https://developers.kakao.com/"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"카카오 개발자사이트"}]},{"type":"text","value":"에가서 가입후 키발급을 받자"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tagName":"h2","properties":{"id":"적용하기","style":"position:relative;"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"a","properties":{"href":"#%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0","ariaLabel":"적용하기 permalink","className":["anchor","before"]},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"svg","properties":{"ariaHidden":"true","focusable":"false","height":"16","version":"1.1","viewBox":"0 0 16 16","width":"16"},"children":[{"type":"element","tagName":"path","properties":{"fillRule":"evenodd","d":"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c